com.github.wuic.exception

Class WuicRuntimeException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • com.github.wuic.exception.WuicRuntimeException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ErrorCode, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BadArgumentException, PollingOperationNotSupportedException, SaveOperationNotSupportedException

    public abstract class WuicRuntimeException
extends RuntimeException
implements ErrorCode

    This exception is a global unchecked exception thrown by WUIC. It is mainly identified with a code defined as a constant in ErrorCode.
